<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I’m following up on my previous attempts to move forward with your business insurance.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I understand that there can be many reasons why you may not be interested right now, and I wanted to check if any of these apply to you.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>Current policy not due to expire?</b><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you let me know your expiry date for your business insurance policy, I can give you a call nearer the time to arrange a new quote.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>Want no further contact?</b><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you are not interested in moving forward, just let me know and I will ensure I don’t contact you again.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, if you are&nbsp;<b>still interested in proceeding</b>, reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively, you can give me a ring on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;">,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>